<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFFC6A43FA949A4D1BFFB7B0" pageId="7" pageNumber="765" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFFC6A43FA949A4D1BFFB7B0" blockId="7.[1383,2593,2183,3282]" pageId="7" pageNumber="765">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFFC6A43FA949A4D18C6B707" bold="true" box="[1384,1734,3092,3125]" pageId="7" pageNumber="765">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The [UCN Red List. The Japanese Noctule is rarely recorded and possibly threatened by deforestation and agricultural expansion.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFFC6A43FA949ACB176FB7E0" pageId="7" pageNumber="765" type="bibRefCitation_list">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFFC6A43FA949ACB176FB7E0" blockId="7.[1383,2593,2183,3282]" pageId="7" pageNumber="765">
